irmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Trentino]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Central Bohemian Region]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| Male\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A man from Central Bohemia who visited Trentino, Italy.<ref name=case37.twitter>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/adamvojtechano/status/1237136521444167692|title=Minister of Health announces case 37|website=Twitter/AdamVojtech|access-date=2020-03-09}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''38'''\n| 9 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Failure|Community spread}}\n| {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Prague]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| {{Partial failure|[[Bulovka Hospital]], [[Prague]]}}\n| Male\n| 40\u201345\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A Prague [[Uber]] driver with no travel history and no known connection to other cases; however, German nationals he was in contact with are investigated. It is the first community spread case in the Czech Republic.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.idnes.cz/zpravy/domaci/koronavirus-cesko-taxikar-komunita-prymula-sireni-infekce-karantena.A200309_230610_domaci_remy|title=Ztr\u00e1ta kontroly nad koronavirem? Taxik\u00e1\u0159 je zlomov\u00fd p\u0159\u00edpad, \u0159ekl Prymula|date=2020-03-09|website=iDNES.cz|access-date=2020-03-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.irozhlas.cz/zpravy-domov/koronavirus-taxikar-praha-nakaza-sireni-karantena_2003101401_kno|title=\u0158idi\u010d Uberu byl podle hygieny v kontaktu s t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 stovkou lid\u00ed. Nakazit ho mohli n\u011bme\u010dt\u00ed klienti Airbnb|website=iROZHLAS}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''39'''\n| 10 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Partial failure|Person-to-person spread}}\n| {{flagicon|CZE}} workplace\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Central Bohemian Region]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| Female\n| ~61\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A woman